{"tid":270871,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Intern就係請廉價勞工","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T19:10:08.000Z","uid":57076,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97ba7ee17bea17eb50b6f0f523798be9f4f37eac","tid":270871,"uid":57076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得做intern可以提高你比個間公司請既機會。<br />\n唔好傻啦，如果你唔係做big4/I-bank/政府intern，其他都係做狗咋，有D仲要無人工，請你去做義工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要洗人唔洗本，當你狗咁看待，跟住你做完下年繼續請新一堆人做。<br />\n<br />\n所謂intern，好多都係以intern名義請班低過最低工資既廉價勞工。咁刻薄法就算日後真係請翻你，你覺得人工會高？大學生有腦點解要做？"},{"pid":"d5bf3a80f9a599d71bee679f463e53c651d4cfe7","tid":270871,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"各取所需"},{"pid":"209269901df9c82a1d2e2bdcd1f8fc7945d5bdd6","tid":270871,"uid":57076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各取所需</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無人工可以點取所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee67aceed04a699dbb57cd1967b89b544dd0650e","tid":270871,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各取所需</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無人工可以點取所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數都有幾千蚊"},{"pid":"8e758c3dd6cfbbc07a96b773188a1e83b0145e19","tid":270871,"uid":79763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"有啲intern無錢 啲人都照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8f6e9ae8f261ce50c3e6d17e6398eba3a37c0e","tid":270871,"uid":62837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"日後見長工又要你有intern<br />\n都唔知邊個發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係d友仔做壞晒"},{"pid":"ac48fe4b0d3449dbf251251708671c6879170b1e","tid